TWComponent.script: tw.local.sqlStatement select distinct LP."NAME" as ApplicationName, LP.SHORT_NAME as ProjectAcronym, LUX.USER_NAME as LastModifiedByUser, count(*) as UnnamedSnapshotCount from LSW_SNAPSHOT LS, LSW_PROJECT LP, LSW_USR_XREF LUX where LS."NAME" is null and LS.PROJECT_ID = LP.PROJECT_ID and LUX.USER_ID = LS.LAST_MODIFIED_BY_USER_ID group by LP."NAME", LP.SHORT_NAME, LUX.USER_NAME order by UnnamedSnapshotCount desc
